Musician: Hey, Akito! Toya! Make sure you give those two a good thrashing tonight!
Akito: Oh, it's you.
Akito: That'll all depend on how they perform tonight. Anyway, we'll see you inside.
Musician: There'll be no more riding her father's coattails after going up against the BAD DOGS. I can't wait to see her get shown up in front of an audience.
Musician: All right, time to get ready to lend my support.
