Akito: Hey, what happened? Is there something wrong with the equipment?
Spectator A: Hey, what gives? Things were just getting good...
Spectator B: Something happen with the sound system?
Kohane: (Wh-What do we do?! The music stopped and the mics aren't working!)
An: (This is bad! If we don't do something, it's going to kill the mood!)
An: (Is Kohane all right?)
Kohane: .....
An: (She's letting the mood of the room get to her. I can't blame her, though. This is her first event.)
An: (All the more reason I can't let this get ruined.)
An: (If we're going to surpass RAD WEEKEND together, we can't let something like this trip us up!)
An: ♪——!
